data.description: This spacious three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom patio home in Sharpstown offers comfort and convenience. The formal living room and dining room provide spaces for entertaining. A cozy family room, perfect for casual gatherings and movie nights. The family room flows into the kitchen with ample counter and cabinet space and seamlessly flows into a bright and airy breakfast room, creating a warm and inviting space to enjoy your morning coffee or casual meals. The primary suite features a spacious layout, a private ensuite bathroom, and a walk-in closet. The primary en suite with dual sinks, vanity space, a separate shower, and a whirlpool tub, a place where one can unwind and relax. Upstairs, two secondary bedrooms share a full bathroom. Outside, the patio area provides a retreat, perfect for unwinding after a long day. This home offers easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major highways, making it the perfect place to call home. Schedule your private showing today!
